name: Strapwire
tagline: A deliciously simple wireframing kit based on the Bootstrap 3 grid
body: # Wirestrap ## A deliciously simple wireframing kit based on the Bootstrap 3 grid ### Prerequisites 1. Mac OS X 10.10+ 2. Sketch 3.8.2 ### How to use 1. Clone this repo to your computer 2. Download the required fonts: Lato and BLOKK 3. Open the Sketch file
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
